## 5. Pseudocode

```
i = 0

function build(preorder, min, max):
    if i >= size:
        return NULL

    if preorder[i] < min OR preorder[i] > max:
        return NULL

    node = new Node(preorder[i])
    i++

    node.left = build(preorder, min, node.val)
    node.right = build(preorder, node.val, max)

    return node
```

